{
  "texts": [
    "The overall conclusion from this review is that the combination of iVR and wearable biosensors is a field with a promising future.",
    "Over coming years, research into using both technologies together will increase significantly, especially, in applications that use biosensor data to modify and to adapt the experience to the needs of the user.",
    "Developments that will also be driven through improvements to both HMD quality and rapid wearable biosensor connections.",
    "In addition, other technologies such as AI for data analysis will be incorporated to make this process simpler and more systematic.",
    "The combination of wearable biosensors and iVR provides a tool from which many benefits can be obtained, especially when biofeedback is included."
  ]
}